dth: 1025px)\" \/><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"bmjsw TmzDJ DXqUA UMBA UbGlr  hsDdd \" draggable=\"false\" src=\"https:\/\/i.natgeofe.com\/n\/77d9a1bc-a62a-4c0d-967f-f6c94130c369\/MM8327_R280B_FR_19_square.jpg\" alt=\"a child receiving a dose of cannabidiol\" data-testid=\"prism-image\" \/><\/picture><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><button class=\"xjUSk NatTH NqeUA dZTKY QMxMQ XbEWk hswTp nkbp lIDy hUQGO gWRci aNnIu GDslh LpcJi wardV kcRqD fhCRd MYLFX RkJsE iEOQC yaNWn ZUpvj HoXXr  mLASH egFzk qXWHA ScoIf bnIxg jIRH wNxoc OJpwZ BOFPn wSPfd ofvJb bMrzT YIauu gGlNh ARCOA kyjTO xqlN aANqO aNnIu GDslh LjPJo RpDvg YYtC rTpcz EDgo UVTAB oxVnu sXtkB AAqU fctVp ENhiS kCffO \" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Open Fullscreen\" data-testid=\"prism-ImageViewer_ExpandButton\"><\/button><figcaption>\n<div class=\"nMMea bNYiy Mjgpa dGwha DDmxa jgKNG RGHCC aBIU PriDW lZur tSkSq \" data-testid=\"prism-caption\">\n<div class=\"HXPPJ barbu IzgMt VcHIt uhSzI YGNMU cRAsZ xqMcl QtRul \"><span class=\"hsDdd OOSI GpQCA lZur VlFaz \" data-testid=\"prism-truncate\"><span class=\"gtOSm FbbUW tUtYa vOCwz EQwFq yCufu eEak Qmvg nyTIa SRXVc vzLa jgBfc WXDas CiUCW kqbG zrdEG txGfn ygKVe BbezD UOtxr CVfpq xijV soGRS XgdC sEIlf daWqJ \">Lily Rowland receives a dose of an oil derived mainly from cannabidiol (CBD), a nonpsychoactive substance in marijuana. She used to suffer hundreds of seizures with violent convulsions every day. Her family moved to Colorado, which voted to legalize marijuana in 2012, so that she could begin a daily regimen.<\/span><\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"lZur asrEW \">\n<figure class=\"kzIjN GNmeK pYrtp dSqFO \" data-testid=\"prism-figure\">\n<div class=\"GpQCA lZur \" data-testid=\"prism-ratio-frame\">\n<div class=\"FvQLF iLTd NqeUA UzzHi iWsMV \"><picture data-testid=\"prism-picture\"><source srcset=\"https:\/\/i.natgeofe.com\/n\/7f162ace-a242-446a-b45e-01b77a2c33f7\/MM8327_R304A_FR_06_square.jpg?w=374&amp;h=374, https:\/\/i.natgeofe.com\/n\/7